    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，PersonOfInterest应该是核心追踪对象对吧？那它下面具体要挂哪些属性？我看到您提到了emails和repos，还有其他的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PersonOfInterest",
        "emails",
        "repos"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，PersonOfInterest要全一点，除了emails和repos，还要有companies、social accounts、phone numbers、org memberships，另外很重要的一点是Credentials——这个人的凭证信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PersonOfInterest",
        "companies",
        "social accounts",
        "phone numbers",
        "org memberships",
        "Credentials"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，PersonOfInterest的分支我加上了。现在看GitHubOrg这块，我理解是组织层面的信息，下面放Repositories、commits、members对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GitHubOrg",
        "Repositories",
        "commits",
        "members"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。另外GitHubRepo作为单独节点也要展开，它下面要有Committers、branches、forks，同样也要有Credentials——仓库级别的凭证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GitHubRepo",
        "Committers",
        "branches",
        "forks",
        "Credentials"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到。Service这个节点我理解是通用服务层，下面挂Credential，然后Credential再细化成username、token、key、secret这些字段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Service",
        "Credential",
        "username",
        "token",
        "key",
        "secret"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这样设计比较统一。对了，domains那个分支我还想再细化一下，加上subdomains，subdomains下面再套一层nested subdomains，另外domains平级要有EmailAddress和apps。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "domains",
        "subdomains",
