      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部完成了。我检查一下结构：根节点Groupware_IssueTracker下五个主分支，domains带三层嵌套，PersonOfInterest七个子项，GitHubOrg和GitHubRepo各自展开，Service下Credential细化到四个凭证字段。您看还有要调整的吗？",
